        </item>
        <item>
            <title>华为发表原生智能 Harmony Intelligence   官方：首次将 AI 能力深度融入系统</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/22/harmony-intelligence/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=harmony-intelligence</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/22/harmony-intelligence/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 07:00:15 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[应用软件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Harmony Intelligence]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[HarmonyOS NEXT]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[华为]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1245204</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在 2024 年华为开发者大会上，华为推出全新 HarmonyOS NEXT 操作系统，华为表示，这款操作系统的内核已经超越 Linux 内核，并首度将 AI 能力深度融入系统，为用户带来前所未有的智能体验。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1245205 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191058-694x303.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="303" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191058-694x303.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191058.jpg 1194w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1245206 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191102-694x334.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="334" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191102-694x334.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191102.jpg 1114w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><div class="mceTemp"></div><div class="mceTemp"></div><p>华为终端 BG 软件部总裁龚体在演讲中介绍 HarmonyOS NEXT 的创新功能之一，是将 AI 能力深度整合进系统中。这次发布的 AI 功能包括 AIGC 图像生成，如手绘线稿、填色、涂鸦和照片扩图等，还有业界首创的 AI 声音修复功能，专为协助言语障碍人群设计。此外，内置「小艺看世界」功能，可以帮助视障用户「读图」，例如朗读冰箱里的蔬菜种类、放置位置及新鲜程度。</p><p>「小艺智慧助手」也在此次大会上进行了重大升级，成为基于盘古大模型 5.0 的「小艺智能体」。用户无需唤醒助手，只需将内容拖放到手机画面导航列上即可随时召唤，并完成一系列操作，例如生成图表或文本摘要。这些 AI 能力大幅提升了用户的便利性和操作效率。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1245211" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191128-694x269.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="269" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191128-694x269.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191128.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1245207" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191107-694x328.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="328" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191107-694x328.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191107.jpg 1104w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1245208" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191113-694x377.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="377" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191113-694x377.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024062191113.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>HarmonyOS NEXT 内置的「控件 AI 化」特性，允许第三方应用程式调用系统空间，实现实时朗读、智能填充、图文翻译和主体抠图等功能。这些创新功能将极大地提升用户体验，使操作更加直观便捷。</p><p>华为表示，HarmonyOS NEXT 将于 8 月推送普通消费者专用的 Beta 版本。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/776/780.htm">IT 之家</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/22/harmonyos-next-7/software/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">华为：HarmonyOS NEXT 打破欧美垄断，已超越 Linux 内核性能升 10.7% 更流畅更安全</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/20/dnf-removed-from-some-android-application-store/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">腾讯手游 DNF 疑因游戏分佣矛盾　下架华为、OPPO、VIVO 等 Android 商店平台</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/18/harmonyosnext-removed-all-source-code-from-us/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">外媒：华为 HarmonyOS NEXT　将删除与美国有关的所有原始程式码</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/22/harmony-intelligence/ai/">华为发表原生智能 Harmony Intelligence   官方：首次将 AI 能力深度融入系统</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/22/harmony-intelligence/ai/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
