        <item>
            <title>【评测】MG 敍述高达 C 装备 Ver.Ka　骨架高水准表现 + 两副精神框架</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/22/mgntgundam/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mgntgundam</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/22/mgntgundam/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Gary Lee]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 22 Jun 2024 04:30:57 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩具]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1244206</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>虽然 2018 年上映的机动战士高达 NT，评价并不太怎么样，表现算是中规中矩，但 Bandai 是不会放过任何抢钱的机会的，今次推出的 MG，就是剧中的敍述高达 C 装备，亦有三文鱼高达之称，到达会否有什么新惊喜呢？</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245246" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8931-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8931-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8931.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>将近 6 年后，Bandai 终于推出了敍述高达的 KA 版 MG 模型，定价为 7,700 日圆（含税）。由于 NT 高达本体的装备实不多，零件板件量是较少的，大多数的版件都是骨架的组成。其红色的精神框架，是与独角兽高达的骨架配色极为相似，而今次 NT 高达的精神框架就是在纹理处理方面更为优胜，观感更有睇头，更可以用紫外光灯照射时，有特别亮眼的效果。另外亦提供了 MG 独角兽的精神框架，不过却是灰色的，可以还原未启动状态，不过小编来看就不会用此灰色的精神框架了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245247" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8086-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8086-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8086.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245248" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8087-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8087-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8087.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245249" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8088-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8088-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8088.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245250" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8089-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8089-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8089.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245251" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8084-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8084-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8084.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245252" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8090-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8090-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8090.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>说明书方面，新增了组装每个部位时所需要的板件，一目了然非常清楚，而敍述高达的内构部分表现也很出色，手腿部分大量暴露内构，拆除外部装甲即可看到内构的各项细节。而红色的精神框架部分安装在骨架框架和外甲上，使内构形态更完整充实。由于涉及 C 装备的设计，整体结构比预期复杂。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245254" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8096-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8096-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8096.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245253" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8092-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8092-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8092.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>外观细节方面加入了不少 KA 版设计，例如胸口凸起结构和外甲边缘的分色细节，外观非常之有特色，当然 KA 版就一定有 KA 版的专有大量水贴，虽然是水贴地狱，但花点时间贴好后，是非常之靓仔的，这亦是小编一向都很喜爱 KA 版的原因之一。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245255" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8413-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8413-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8413.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245256" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8121-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8121-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8121.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245257" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8122-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8122-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8122.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245258" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8140-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8140-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8140.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245259" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8141-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8141-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8141.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245260" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8165-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8165-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8165.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245261" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8288-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8288-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8288.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245262" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8291-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8291-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8291.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245263" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8300-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8300-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8300.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245264" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8302-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8302-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8302.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245265" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8412-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8412-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8412.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>核心战机造型别致，驾驶舱细节丰富，变形流程相当复杂，腰部和手腿关节需要小心调整，否则容易出现磨损和脱扣情况。外观细节在 MG 化后更加清晰，双 V 型天线和头顶黑色砲口的火神砲细节锐利。胸部设计方面，驾驶舱门可独立展开，腰部可动受到核心战机影响有所限制，手臂和腿部可动性高，手指关节灵活。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245266" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8289-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8289-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8289.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245269" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8109-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8109-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8109.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245267" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8290-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8290-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8290.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245268" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8291-1-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8291-1-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8291-1.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></h2><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245280" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8444-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8444-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8444.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245281" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8777-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8777-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_8777.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>完成图</h2><p><a title="_DSC9435" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53807474104/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53807474104_eb30e662cd_b.j